comment: Plumlee (POR) sets the screen on Mack (UTA) and gives him room to avoid the contact.

There is no angle that definitively shows Mack (UTA) make contact with Lillard (POR) during his upward shooting motion, however if any contact occurs, it does not affect his shooting motion and is not to his arms.
Plumlee (POR) sets the screen on Hood (UTA) and gives him room to avoid the contact. He is firming up and absorbs the contact when it occurs.
Hood (UTA) gathers the ball on his left foot, establishing his pivot. He then drops this foot back when starting his dribble.
Davis (POR) maintains legal guarding position as he defends Favors' (UTA) shot attempt.
After communicating with the Replay Center, the ruling on the court that the ball was last touched by Favors (UTA) prior to going OOB was upheld.
Hood (UTA) commits a take foul on McCollum (POR).
Mack (UTA) commits a take foul on McCollum (POR).
